  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT310-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">varaiviṭai muṉintu kiḻatti tōḻikku uraittatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Told by HER to the confidante, being fed up with
          [awaiting] the time of marriage. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT310">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> puḷḷum pulampiṉa pūvuṅ kūmpiṉa</l>
          <l> kāṉalum pulampunaṉi yuṭaittē vāṉamu</l>
          <l> nammē pōlu mammart tāki</l>
          <l> yellai kaḻiyap pulleṉ ṟaṉṟē</l>
          <l> yiṉṉu muḷeṉē tōḻi yinnilai</l>
          <l> taṇṇiya kamaḻu ñāḻaṟ</l>
          <l> ṟaṇṇan tuṟaivark kuraikkunarp peṟiṉē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>The birds began to lament and the flowers closed</l>
          <l>and the seashore grove is filled with loneliness.</l>
          <l rend="indent9">The sky too,</l>
          <l>just like us , has become difuse</l>
          <l>[and] empty as the daylight passes.</l>
          <l>Even now I am, friend.</l>
          <l rend="indent6">This state,</l>
          <l>if only someone told the man from the cool ghat</l>
          <l>of cool [and] fragrant Ñāḻal trees.</l>

        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
